All Classes

Class Description
Coordinates
Used to define (row, column) coordinates of a point on the tunnel's map
FieldTypes
Enum specifying the possible field values on the tunnel's map.
MapPanel
Class used to show the tunnel's map state in the GUI.
MetroApplication
Application creating a simulation of a metro.
MetroGUI
The main class of this app's GUI.
ModelParameters
Class used to specify parameters of the metro simulation: - trains' wagons - trains' routes - initial order - stations
SimulationModel
A class defining an app simulating the concurrently working metro Use start() method to launch the GUI of the simulation.
StationsLock
Class used to ensure that trains only move when the station's entrance they're headed to is not occupied.
Train
Class representing a concurrent train in the metro
TunnelsMapMonitor
Class used to access the map of the tunnels.
